    "description": "在这款rogue-lite射击游戏中，你要发射炮弹、设置陷阱、击退无情的怪物群，保护小女孩免遭赫拉的迁怒。阿斯特来亚（Astraea） 是一款令人心跳加速的游戏，玩家必须在应对空中各种威胁的情况下阻止地面上的任何东西接近小女孩。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要亮点</h2><br><strong>沉浸式故事情节</strong><br><br>在战斗内外展开的声情并茂、引人入胜的故事中开启沉浸式体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/b65faf8bc467f5b8f9f1c6094306b9ca.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/b65faf8bc467f5b8f9f1c6094306b9ca.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/b65faf8bc467f5b8f9f1c6094306b9ca.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>快速推进</strong><br><br>从宙斯的祝福中进行选择，提升包含准确性和诅咒能力在内的一切技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/149041308965fa5822dff71cb6969e6c.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/149041308965fa5822dff71cb6969e6c.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/149041308965fa5822dff71cb6969e6c.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>更多挑战</strong><br><br>通过解锁难关测试你的技能，完成大量挑战和成就。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d08ebe46a4306a6a5f7b12f291cf4519.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d08ebe46a4306a6a5f7b12f291cf4519.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/d08ebe46a4306a6a5f7b12f291cf4519.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>隐藏的收集要素</strong><br><br>在抵御赫拉爪牙的无情攻击的同时，寻找隐藏的收集要素。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/7b56490a2510afff9e4d8a1d6c6c4e4b.poster.avif?t=1736735334\" width=548 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/7b56490a2510afff9e4d8a1d6c6c4e4b.webm?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314530/extras/7b56490a2510afff9e4d8a1d6c6c4e4b.mp4?t=1736735334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未来更新</h2><br>更多全新敌人、挑战、藏品和游戏模式......值得期待。",
